EXTRACTED VALUE: CoD3 is a game that is slightly repetitive if not lackluster in its single player - the first level is insanely awesome though.
The world is bright and so colorful it almost assaults the senses. The eccentric cast of characters is extremely well detailed and animated.
Polished, involving and a great deal of fun, but current-gen in all but the smallest details. [Oct 2006, p.126]
